OL,3,CWelsh NHS could refuse to offer
OL,4,Cassisted dying services, says minister
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary has confirmed
OL,7,Fthat the Welsh NHS could refuse to
OL,8,Foffer assisted dying services even if
OL,9,Fthey were to be introduced in England.
OL,11,FJeremy Miles said that Senedd members
OL,12,Fwill have the power to block the
OL,13,Fimplementation of the law change
OL,14,Falthough he acknowledged that private
OL,15,Fsector health providers could offer
OL,16,Fsuch a service here in Wales.
