OL,3,CWelsh NHS could refuse to offer
OL,4,Cassisted dying services, says minister
OL,6,FThat in turn raises the prospect of
OL,7,Fassisted dying being legalised here in
OL,8,FWales but Welsh doctors prohibited
OL,9,Ffrom providing the service.
OL,11,FHealth Secretary Jeremy Miles has been
OL,12,Fgiving evidence to the Senedd's Health
OL,13,FCommittee which has been trying to
OL,14,Fgain some clarity about the situation.
OL,16,FMr Miles told the committee that the
OL,17,FWelsh Government has taken a neutral
OL,18,Fposition on the proposals.
