OL,3,CWelsh NHS could refuse to offer
OL,4,Cassisted dying services, says minister
OL,6,FCommittee members raised concerns
OL,7,Fabout confusion if different
OL,8,Fregulations and services were to be
OL,9,Foffered within Wales and across the
OL,10,Fborder in England.
OL,12,FMr Miles said: "I accept, as is quite
OL,13,Foften said, that if you live on the
OL,14,Fborder, perhaps there's more
OL,15,Funcertainty. But as you say, we have
OL,16,Fbeen through a period (the Covid
OL,17,Fpandemic) when the law was clear and
OL,18,Fdifferent on either side of the
OL,19,Fborder, ways of implementing that are
OL,20,Feffective."
